name: There Is No Jam
description:
Made For Minijam 106: Frogs 2

In this game your laptop gets destroyed "mysterious" box, and you need to find a way to get to the laptop and join to Minijam, that has LIMITED TIME... (we incorporated the limitation very well, I know...)

ONLY MOUSE NEEDED

*USE FULLSCREEN!!!*

Inspired by: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1240210/There_Is_No_Game_Wrong_Dimension/
